Name: Therapist
Text: We all make mistakes. I think you should start appreciating yourself, for who you really are.

Name: Therapist
Text: Also, remember to acknowledge that we all are imprefect!

Name: Bieda
Text: Doc, give me some real tips.

Name: Therapist
Text: You can try changing into objects or maybe teleporting?

Name: Bieda
Text: I can't do that! My Creators devoted little time to my development.

Name: Therapist
Text: Speaking about little time. Looks like we are out of time. We will see each other next week!
